Semaphore

wait 		backup will wait as long this file exist
waita 		async-backup will wait as long this file exist
stop		backup will stop as soon as possible
astop		async-backup will stop as soon as possible
switch		switch to next hd in chain
kill 		kills the system with force - not recommended
noautostart	don't start the system after reboot automatically 
skipcrc		skip crc check during copy to ddumbfs (not recommended)
